description:
Water is a block that often confuses and frustrates Minecraft players because it doesn't always work the way you expect it to. Little by little I have learned the traits of this block, which I'm attempting to share with you in this tutorial.

This tutorial covers a lot of well known things about water. It also covers a few things not many people know or understand. I hope it is useful to you.
